title: Extension piece for flow track

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for an extension piece for flow track, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a side view of my extension piece for flow track showing my new design;
FIG. 2 is a side view thereof, with the extension piece attached to a flow track in an extended position;
FIG. 3 is a side view thereof, with the extension piece attached to a flow track in a retracted position;
FIG. 4 is a front view thereof;
FIG. 5 is a perspective view thereof; and,
FIG. 6 is another perspective view thereof.
The broken line showing of a flow track in FIGS. 2–5 is included for the purpose of illustrating environment and forms no part of the claimed design.
